The paper deals with image recognition and caption generation, which are core topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of a knowledge base to handle abstract concepts suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. The paper also proposes a two-step process involving attention and inference, which are common techniques in machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
